      "profile": "delivery",
      "reqId": "CAT-DEL-2",
      "level": "MUST",
      "statement": "An AssessmentResult MUST identify the result and section, list the items attempted (with attempt number), and state whether continuation is required; it carries the candidate response and outcome variables.",
